===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*krap|t=to beat, thrash, winnow}}, which is distantly related (via an [[allofam]]) to {{cog|my|ယပ်|t=fan}}, and more directly to the following Sinitic words (STEDT):
* {{och-l|躐|to tread, trample}}
* {{och-l|押|to seal, stamp}}
* {{och-l|臿|pestle; to husk grain with a mortar and pestle}}

